### CHECKLIST MANUALE DOPO I TEST
### =====================================================================
###
### ✅ 1.1  → 201, body { id, username, name, surname } (NO salt/password)
### ✅ 1.4  → 401
### ✅ 1.8  → 401
### ✅ 1.9  → 200, dati utente
### ✅ 1.10 → 200 o 204
### ✅ 2.1  → 200, { lines:[...], stations:[...], connections:[...] }
### ✅ 2.2  → 401
### ✅ 3.1  → 200, array [ { id, username, best_score }, ... ] ordinato DESC
### ✅ 4.1  → 201, { gameId, startStation:{id,name}, endStation:{id,name} }
###           startStation.id ≠ endStation.id
### ✅ 5.1  → 200, { valid:true, segments:[...], finalScore: >= 0 }
### ✅ 5.2  → 409
### ✅ 5.3  → 200, { valid:false, segments:[], finalScore:0 }
### ✅ 5.7  → 400
### ✅ 5.8  → 400
### ✅ 5.9  → 400
### ✅ 5.13 → 404
### ✅ 5.14 → 400
### ✅ 5.15 → 404
### ✅ 5.18 → finalScore >= 0 sempre
